Package dev.cookiecode.maven.plugin.protobuf

Class ProtocTestCompileJavaScriptMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • dev.cookiecode.maven.plugin.protobuf.AbstractProtocMojo
        • dev.cookiecode.maven.plugin.protobuf.AbstractProtocTestCompileMojo
          • dev.cookiecode.maven.plugin.protobuf.ProtocTestCompileJavaScriptMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextEnabled, Mojo
    @Mojo(name="test-compile-js",
      defaultPhase=GENERATE_TEST_SOURCES,
      requiresDependencyResolution=TEST,
      threadSafe=true)
public final class ProtocTestCompileJavaScriptMojo
extends AbstractProtocTestCompileMojo
    This mojo executes the protoc compiler for generating test JavaScript sources from protocol buffer definitions. It also searches dependency artifacts in the test scope for .proto files and includes them in the proto_path so that they can be referenced. Finally, it adds the .proto files to the project as test resources so that they can be included in the test-jar artifact.
    Since:
    0.6.0
